<p>&quot;I know, I know.&quot; Clef got up and put his pants back on, thudding down at the computer. &quot;I'm gonna have to add this to the experiment log, you do realize.&quot;</p>
<p>&quot;Please don't name me in it.&quot;</p>
<p>&quot;Well I don't wanna name myself either! I'm the fucking project head!&quot;</p>
<p>&quot;Okay, fine, just blame it all on me then-&quot;</p>
<p>&quot;I told the other researchers it'd be you doing it-&quot;</p>
